Third-Party Licenses

MSI Extensions compile with several 3rd party components used under the following licenses.

Boost

Boost provides free peer-reviewed portable C++ source libraries under the Boost License.

CppUnit

CppUnit is the C++ port of JUnit framework that provides C++ unit testing under the GNU Lesser General Public License.

Crypto++

Crypto++ Library is a free C++ class library that provides cryptographic schemes under the Crypto++ License.

Tclap Command-Line Parser

TCLAP is a small, flexible library that provides a simple interface for defining and accessing command line arguments under the MIT License.
